+### noisy git wrapper
+
+Regression: a git wrapper writing progress to stdout must not leak into generated scripts.
+
+```zsh
+% function git { echo "noisy git wrapper"; mockgit "$@" }
+% antidote-script --kind clone bar/foo 2>/dev/null
+% ! antidote-script --kind clone bar/foo 2>&1 | grep -q "noisy git wrapper"
+% antidote-script --kind clone bar/foo 2>&1 | grep -q "# antidote cloning"
+% unfunction git
+%
+```
+
